OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1772193824
OL,3,CCouncil to pay compensation to family
OL,4,Cover SEND education failures
OL,6,FA North East council has agreed to pay
OL,7,Falmost #6,000 to a family, after an
OL,8,Fombudsman found it failed to provide
OL,9,Fpromised specialist technology that
OL,10,Fwould have allowed a child with
OL,11,Fspecial educational needs to learn
OL,12,Ffrom home.
OL,14,FThe child had not attended school
OL,15,Fsince September 2022 due to their
OL,16,Fspecial educational needs.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
