CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1772193824
OL,3,CCouncil to pay compensation to family
OL,4,Cover SEND education failures
OL,6,FMark Mirfin, Director of Children's
OL,7,FServices at North Tyneside Council,
OL,8,Fhas said the authority accepts the
OL,9,Fombudsman's findings in full
OL,11,FA provision has been in place for the
OL,12,Fchild since March 2025.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/7
